    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is honestly in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, you\u2019d think it was brand new! Not a scratch or a smudge anywhere, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants that new-car feel without the new-car price tag. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
