    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This example boasts a pristine Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically optimized, it has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cabin is free of common wear points like bolster fatigue or trim delamination. A turn-key, mechanically transparent masterpiece for the serious driver.",
      "price": 47500.0,
