      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it\u2019s brand new! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it runs like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. You\u2019re going to love how it looks in your driveway!",
